videos.description: Nate Sestina kicks the ball out to Ashton Hagans who hits a 3 to put Kentucky ahead 10-0 to start the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hagans' 3 caps Kentucky's 10-0 run to start game) 2019/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hagans' 3 caps Kentucky's 10-0 run to start game

videos.description: Tyrese Maxey floats the ball to Nick Richards who leaps above the Lamar defender to slam down a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Maxey sets up Richards for alley-oop slam) 2019/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Maxey sets up Richards for alley-oop slam

videos.description: Kentucky is able to turn things around from the 3-point line, hitting seven times in the first 17 minutes of the game in the Wildcats win vs. Lamar on Sunday.
